===Noun===
{{en-noun|-|s}}

# The absence of any [[sound]].
#: {{ux|en|When the motor stopped, the '''silence''' was almost deafening.}}
#* {{quote-song|en|title=Enjoy the Silence|album=Violator|year=1990|artist=Depeche Mode|author=Martin L. Gore|authorlink=Martin Gore|passage=Words like violence break the '''silence''' / Come crashing in into my little world}}
